{
  "stem": "3212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's so hard to understand this-- how could it be that all the people are against us, that we couldn't find somebody to help us or to be with us or to offer a good word for us?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was very hard to find somebody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In our house, we had another family-- that she was Jewish, Mrs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Stiegler.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and my-- and she had a son, Pauli, that they were half-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my brother found a good friend in this Pauli.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That--and sometimes she invited us-- she had probably more food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She invited us kids to come to her house to eat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I never forget her name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And later on, I found out that her son is living still today in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he told me stories about my brother that I never knew, that-- what he did with him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were really friends.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It started-- slowly, all our family except my cousin that worked in the Jewish community and my uncle with his sister and my cousins from Walter, that we didn't almost have nobody, because slowly they sent everybody.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The [NON-ENGLISH] that lived in our apartment with their three children were sent away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Tante Rose--- that her daughter committed suicide and her husband died-- she was sent away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were round up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came to pick them up-- the SS-- and took them away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Later on, I found out the [NON-ENGLISH] probably were sent, too, to Poland, where they were killed, or to Auschwitz, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Tante Rose was sent to Theresienstadt, to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even my cousin's son that worked for the Jewish Community, Otto Bock, his mother and father had to be sent away.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even he couldn't help them to stay in Vienna.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
